    {
      "type": "note",
      "id": "J2GYl1",
      "x": 1860,
      "y": 1602,
      "name": "Note — Catalog search contract",
      "width": 460,
      "height": 0,
      "content": "Catalog search: the rail is a curated everyday subset (name, text, set, color, type, rarity, MV) — deliberately NOT Scryfall's full advanced-search form. The query bar targets full Scryfall syntax. Sync: rail and query are two views over one search state; only rail-recognized terms reflect into the rail, unrecognized terms are preserved verbatim in the query. Contract spec: specs/catalog-search.md (draft)."
    },
